412
00:15:51,280 --> 00:15:52,630
Why did you hit my car?

413
00:15:52,870 --> 00:15:53,920
Do you know what car this is?

414
00:15:53,940 --> 00:15:55,010
Can you afford to pay if you damage it?

415
00:15:55,130 --> 00:15:56,130
Your car?

416
00:15:56,570 --> 00:15:57,380
Bah!

417
00:15:57,490 --> 00:15:59,850
Didn't you even check whose name is on the vehicle registration?

418
00:16:01,230 --> 00:16:01,820
Zhang Xiaoguang,

419
00:16:02,010 --> 00:16:03,370
we'll settle our accounts later.

420
00:16:04,120 --> 00:16:05,790
But today, give me my car back.

421
00:16:05,790 --> 00:16:08,000
Our accounts have already been settled when we broke up.

422
00:16:08,210 --> 00:16:09,610
You still owe me hundreds of thousands.

423
00:16:10,290 --> 00:16:12,170
This car is part of the debt repayment.

424
00:16:12,790 --> 00:16:14,030
Qian, get in the car. Let's go.

425
00:16:14,270 --> 00:16:15,060
Zhang Xiaoguang,

426
00:16:15,350 --> 00:16:16,960
don't think I don't know

427
00:16:16,980 --> 00:16:17,770
what you did with my dad.

428
00:16:17,920 --> 00:16:18,790
In the Huanghai project,

429
00:16:19,080 --> 00:16:20,600
how many freight cars of goods

430
00:16:20,620 --> 00:16:22,430
did you get approved under my dad's name?

431
00:16:22,670 --> 00:16:24,840
And how much crude oil did you get in the Dadong project?

432
00:16:25,130 --> 00:16:26,860
I won't count them one by one.

433
00:16:27,390 --> 00:16:28,200
Go.

434
00:16:28,370 --> 00:16:30,170
Eat your fill. Bon appétit.

435
00:16:30,430 --> 00:16:32,270
Because when you end up in jail,

436
00:16:32,320 --> 00:16:33,600
you won't find any restaurants there.

437
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:34,670
And you,

438
00:16:35,000 --> 00:16:36,630
take care of yourself.

439
00:16:36,790 --> 00:16:38,280
So you'll have the strength to bring him his meals.

440
00:16:41,130 --> 00:16:41,930
What do you want?

441
00:16:42,720 --> 00:16:43,550
Just go.

442
00:16:43,950 --> 00:16:44,870
I'll go to the Discipline Inspection Commission

443
00:16:44,890 --> 00:16:46,830
right after you leave.

444
00:16:48,910 --> 00:16:50,480
Mr. Dong, well,

445
00:16:50,600 --> 00:16:52,270
we've also brought the contract

446
00:16:52,390 --> 00:16:53,960
for the individual case today.

447
00:16:54,050 --> 00:16:55,090
Why don't you take a look?

448
00:16:56,230 --> 00:16:57,980
[Agency Agreement]

449
00:16:56,700 --> 00:16:58,100
You're really well prepared.

450
00:17:03,600 --> 00:17:06,000
Your agency fee is quite high, though.

451
00:17:06,030 --> 00:17:06,680
Is that so?

452
00:17:08,089 --> 00:17:09,849
The contract I signed with Liangcheng Law Firm

453
00:17:09,869 --> 00:17:11,660
was for legal consultancy for an entire year.

454
00:17:12,280 --> 00:17:14,230
And you're asking 600,000 for just one case.

455
00:17:14,920 --> 00:17:15,950
Isn't that a bit too expensive?

456
00:17:16,310 --> 00:17:17,109
Mr. Dong,

457
00:17:17,790 --> 00:17:19,200
let's discuss each case individually.

458
00:17:22,869 --> 00:17:23,550
How about this?

459
00:17:24,589 --> 00:17:27,589
Let's do as you suggested and discuss each case individually—500,000.

460
00:17:31,970 --> 00:17:33,340
Don't get a headache.

461
00:17:34,070 --> 00:17:34,550
I didn't.

462
00:17:34,550 --> 00:17:35,830
Hear me out.

463
00:17:35,870 --> 00:17:36,390
Please, go ahead.

464
00:17:36,410 --> 00:17:37,090
Well,

465
00:17:37,430 --> 00:17:39,040
if we win the first trial

466
00:17:39,480 --> 00:17:40,640
and the other party appeals,

467
00:17:41,300 --> 00:17:44,100
I'll give you an additional 300,000. How does that sound?

468
00:17:46,460 --> 00:17:47,870
Is it necessary?

469
00:17:50,230 --> 00:17:50,880
Yingzi.

470
00:17:51,900 --> 00:17:53,000
We've been working

471
00:17:53,000 --> 00:17:54,100
with Mr. Dong

472
00:17:54,120 --> 00:17:55,240
for a year now.

473
00:17:55,240 --> 00:17:55,920
Yes.

474
00:17:56,070 --> 00:17:58,640
Besides, his company had a tough time

475
00:17:58,880 --> 00:18:00,480
last year,

476
00:18:00,960 --> 00:18:02,720
and this case is going to trial next week.

477
00:18:02,930 --> 00:18:04,570
