478
00:18:04,600 --> 00:18:05,100
Yes.

479
00:18:05,120 --> 00:18:06,050
I think

480
00:18:06,810 --> 00:18:07,920
our economic interests

481
00:18:07,950 --> 00:18:09,120
can be set aside.

482
00:18:09,480 --> 00:18:11,010
Providing good service to the client

483
00:18:11,040 --> 00:18:12,090
is what really matters.

484
00:18:12,110 --> 00:18:12,550
Yes.

485
00:18:12,830 --> 00:18:13,830
Wait, Mr. Dong.

486
00:18:14,330 --> 00:18:16,480
