487
00:18:16,510 --> 00:18:17,830
I'm so pissed.

488
00:18:17,850 --> 00:18:18,350
Are you?

489
00:18:18,610 --> 00:18:19,090
Yes.

490
00:18:19,130 --> 00:18:20,290
Now we're talking.

491
00:18:20,310 --> 00:18:23,420
