492
00:18:23,480 --> 00:18:24,040
Okay.

493
00:18:24,230 --> 00:18:26,030
Change this 600,000 to 500,000.

494
00:18:26,060 --> 00:18:26,500
Alright.

495
00:18:26,520 --> 00:18:27,080
Give me a pen.

496
00:18:29,360 --> 00:18:30,560
Sign here.

497
00:18:30,680 --> 00:18:31,050
Okay.

498
00:18:31,080 --> 00:18:31,470
Here.

499
00:18:31,490 --> 00:18:32,250
