500
00:18:32,280 --> 00:18:33,080
Yes, you need to sign,

501
00:18:33,100 --> 00:18:34,260
so it'll be legally valid.

502
00:18:37,460 --> 00:18:38,450
Yingzi, Yingzi, Yingzi.

503
00:18:38,480 --> 00:18:39,440
Should I sign above your signature?

504
00:18:39,440 --> 00:18:41,140
Mr. Dong knows. He knows where to sign.

505
00:18:41,170 --> 00:18:42,170
Yes, just sign here.

506
00:18:42,190 --> 00:18:42,700
Okay.

507
00:18:46,770 --> 00:18:48,090
Oh my, Luo Yingzi.

508
00:18:48,110 --> 00:18:48,590
Who...

509
00:18:48,950 --> 00:18:50,840
