510
00:18:50,910 --> 00:18:51,860
You're so greedy.

511
00:18:52,410 --> 00:18:53,510
Mr. Chen Shuo.

512
00:18:54,170 --> 00:18:55,380
Why are you here?

513
00:18:55,410 --> 00:18:56,380
I'm here for Mr. Dong.

514
00:18:57,280 --> 00:18:58,040
Excuse me, Mr. Dong.

515
00:18:58,060 --> 00:18:58,820
Let me introduce myself.

516
00:18:59,700 --> 00:19:01,040
I'm a lawyer from Liangcheng Law Firm.

517
00:19:01,410 --> 00:19:02,570
Since this case was signed

518
00:19:02,600 --> 00:19:03,890
with Liangcheng Law Firm

519
00:19:04,350 --> 00:19:05,750
and both Ms. Qiu and Ms. Luo

520
00:19:05,750 --> 00:19:06,460
have left,

521
00:19:06,490 --> 00:19:07,120
our firm

522
00:19:07,510 --> 00:19:08,110
assigned me

523
00:19:08,130 --> 00:19:10,130
to handle your case.

524
00:19:10,240 --> 00:19:10,890
My name is Chen Shuo.

525
00:19:11,700 --> 00:19:12,290
Okay.

526
00:19:13,450 --> 00:19:14,160
Mr. Chen,

527
00:19:14,180 --> 00:19:15,620
