528
00:19:15,830 --> 00:19:16,660
I went to find Mr. Dong,

529
00:19:16,680 --> 00:19:17,810
and they told me he was here,

530
00:19:17,840 --> 00:19:18,670
so I came here.

531
00:19:19,550 --> 00:19:21,030
Mr. Chen, you may not know,

532
00:19:21,310 --> 00:19:22,630
but Mr. Dong has already

533
00:19:22,650 --> 00:19:23,820
entrusted this case to us.

534
00:19:23,850 --> 00:19:25,810
But he hasn't signed, has he?

535
00:19:25,830 --> 00:19:26,870
That's because you came.

536
00:19:28,100 --> 00:19:29,820
Also, this case

537
00:19:29,850 --> 00:19:31,440
is a patent dispute.

538
00:19:31,600 --> 00:19:32,490
As far as I know,

539
00:19:32,510 --> 00:19:33,550
after we left,

540
00:19:33,640 --> 00:19:35,250
Liangcheng Law Firm seemed

541
00:19:35,620 --> 00:19:37,010
to lose its advantage in this field.

542
00:19:37,180 --> 00:19:38,660
