543
00:19:38,710 --> 00:19:39,840
But since I came,

544
00:19:39,960 --> 00:19:41,520
the situation has changed.

545
00:19:42,110 --> 00:19:42,920
Mr. Dong,

546
00:19:43,210 --> 00:19:44,340
you may not know,

547
00:19:44,570 --> 00:19:47,050
