548
00:19:48,030 --> 00:19:48,720
for Huisheng last year.

549
00:19:49,000 --> 00:19:50,330
So, give me three days,

550
00:19:50,390 --> 00:19:51,630
and I promise I'll give you

551
00:19:51,650 --> 00:19:53,170
a very solid representation plan.

552
00:19:53,300 --> 00:19:54,410
I know about that case.

553
00:19:54,630 --> 00:19:55,590
So, you were their attorney?

554
00:19:55,610 --> 00:19:56,240
Yes, it was me.

555
00:19:56,730 --> 00:19:57,490
Mr. Dong,

556
00:19:57,670 --> 00:19:59,390
all the materials and evidence for your case

557
00:19:59,410 --> 00:20:01,540
are still in Liangcheng Law Firm.

558
00:20:01,800 --> 00:20:02,490
As for them,

559
00:20:02,510 --> 00:20:03,600
they didn't even take a single piece of paper.

